txt.en: Hlóthi is in Annak-khurfu in southern Elderslade.\n\nReturn to Hlóthi.

'While you are out among the enemy, keep your eyes open for any correspondences that might give to us some insight into their operations. Anything you can find could give us the edge when we plan our attacks.'
'Excellent work, [placeholder]. These may just give us the advantage we need!'
'Have you found the Orkish orders yet?'
Intercepting Orkish correspondences will give the Gabil'akkâ insight into the plans of the enemy.
March on Gundabad: Pilfering Orkish Orders
Orkish orders can be found across the War of Three Peaks.\n\nYou should gather Orkish orders to help the Gabil'akkâ's cause.
